      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET AGRIPPINA (2) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins and two placings. Hit the frame latest (22.88) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Expected to be in the finish. JUST A MELODY (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (28.01) at this track behind Chicken Fish in a Grade 5/6. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Will give a great sight again. MOO MOVE (7) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a half a length second (22.86) behind ELITE CRACKER at this track. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and two minor placings from three starts. Leading chance. CRENSHAW KING (4) has ability and can find the frame.",
